 sc0 ls0 ws0">here is means </div><div class="t m678 x7 h28 y597 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enough in the hands </div><div class="t m4f8 x7 h28 y974 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of believers to amply </div><div class="t m522 x7 h28 y1fe ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sustain the work in all </div><div class="t m679 x7 h28 y975 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">its departments without embarrassing any, </div><div class="t m636 x8f h28 y676 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">if all would bear their </div><div class="t m256 x9d h28 y976 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proportional part.&quot; </div><div class="t m225 x5e h28 y205 ff7 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Testimonies to the Church, </div><div class="t m1d8 x92 h28 y695 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vol. 3, p. 410. </div><div class="t m35e xa5 h2a y1b3 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">89 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
